Source: @SOURCE_PACKAGE@
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), @ORIOLEPG_PACKAGE@ (>= @ORIOLEPG_VERSION@), @ORIOLEPG_PACKAGE@ (<< @ORIOLEPG_NEXT_VERSION@), libcurl4-openssl-dev (>= 7), libzstd-dev, libssl-dev
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/orioledb/orioledb

Package: @SOURCE_PACKAGE@
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, @ORIOLEPG_PACKAGE@ (>= @ORIOLEPG_VERSION@), @ORIOLEPG_PACKAGE@ (<< @ORIOLEPG_NEXT_VERSION@)
Description: Modern cloud-native storage engine extension for patched PostgreSQL
 OrioleDB is a new storage engine for PostgreSQL, bringing a modern approach
 to database capacity, capabilities and performance to the world's most-loved database platform.
 This extension works on patched version (@PATCHSET_LABEL@) of PostgreSQL @PG_UPSTREAM_VERSION@.
